
This directory holds a work-in-progress spec file for transiting 
the current make packages solution into a single spec file.

DO NOT USE THIS SPEC FILE TO BUILD RPM PACKAGES !

This spec file will not work at the moment.


----

Hint:

for name in `ls ../plugins | grep -v Makefile`;  do \
	echo "%package: "$name; \
	echo "%files"; \
	echo "%defattr(-,root,root)"; \
	echo "\$RPM_BUILD_ROOT/usr/lib/openqrm/"$name; \
	echo ""; \
done
